INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (1,'Experience clear and immersive sound with these Nintendo Classic Wired Earphones. Designed in a sleek white finish with iconic Nintendo-inspired styling, these earphones offer comfortable in-ear fit and high-quality audio performance. Perfect for gaming, music, and everyday use, they come with a durable cable and standard 3.5mm jack for wide compatibility with smartphones, tablets, and gaming devices.',16,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71pyhnTkPBL._AC_UY218_.jpg','Nintendo Classic Wired Earphones ',2999.00,2,'EAR-NIN-001',11,'Audio'),(2,'Stay connected and track your fitness in style with the Samsung Galaxy Watch 8 Classic. Featuring a premium design with a rotating bezel, this smartwatch offers advanced health monitoring including heart rate tracking, sleep analysis, and fitness insights. Powered by Wear OS, it supports apps, notifications, and seamless smartphone connectivity. With a vibrant display and long-lasting battery, it’s perfect for both daily wear and active lifestyles.',20,'https://www.sammobile.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Galaxy-Watch-8-Classic-4-1-1200x675.jpg','Samsung Galaxy Watch 8 Classic',24999.00,2,'SM-WATCH8-CLASSIC-001',10,'Fitness'),(3,'The Oppo A16 is a stylish and reliable smartphone designed for smooth everyday performance. Equipped with 4GB RAM and 64GB internal storage, it handles multitasking and app usage efficiently. The device features a large 6.52-inch display for an immersive viewing experience and a long-lasting 5000mAh battery to keep you powered throughout the day. Its AI triple rear camera setup captures clear photos, while the sleek design ensures a comfortable grip. Perfect for users looking for performance, battery life, and affordability in one device.',20,'https://5.imimg.com/data5/SELLER/Default/2021/12/CF/SL/FD/2900638/oppo-a16-4gb-64rom--500x500.jpg','Oppo A16 ',16000.00,2,'OPPO-A16-4GB-001',26,'Mobiles'),(4,'Upgrade your wardrobe with the Ralph Lauren Premium Polo Shirt, a perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and timeless style. Crafted from high-quality breathable fabric, this shirt offers a soft feel and all-day comfort. Featuring the iconic Ralph Lauren logo, a classic collar design, and a tailored fit, it is ideal for both casual and semi-formal occasions. Pair it with jeans or chinos for a sophisticated look.',20,'https://assets.myntassets.com/w_412,q_50,,dpr_3,fl_progressive,f_webp/assets/images/19846030/2022/9/8/79eea5e3-0ba9-4a0b-9903-282adde9fe631662606196562Shirts1.jpg','Ralph Lauren Premium Polo Shirt',9000.01,2,'RL-SHIRT-001',24,'Fashion'),(5,'Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser is a dermatologist-recommended face wash specially designed for sensitive and dry skin. Its mild, non-irritating formula effectively removes dirt, oil, and impurities without stripping the skin’s natural moisture. Enriched with hydrating ingredients, it helps maintain the skin’s natural barrier while leaving it soft, smooth, and refreshed. Suitable for daily use, this cleanser is perfect for maintaining healthy and balanced skin.',20,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQrN8ZS4Kc_PEH5hiXzg04ZPV44gj26Mxbbng&s','Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser Face Wash',1000.00,2,'CET-FACEWASH-001',18,'Beauty'),(6,'Add style and functionality to your space with this Modern LED Table Lamp. Designed with a sleek and compact look, it provides bright and energy-efficient lighting perfect for study, work, or bedside use. The lamp features a durable build, easy on/off operation, and a warm, eye-friendly light that reduces strain during long hours. Ideal for home, office, or dorm rooms, this table lamp combines practicality with modern design.',20,'https://www.homesake.in/cdn/shop/files/IH0F143-PJT-1-Theme.jpg?v=1748346148','Modern LED Table Lamp',2000.00,2,'TBL-LAMP-001',50,'Home'),(7,'Experience next-level performance with the Apple iPhone 17, designed with cutting-edge technology and a sleek premium finish. Featuring a powerful processor for ultra-fast performance, a stunning high-resolution display, and an advanced camera system for professional-quality photos and videos. With improved battery life, enhanced security features, and seamless iOS experience, the iPhone 17 delivers both style and innovation. Perfect for everyday use, photography, gaming, and productivity.',20,'https://tse2.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP.pSUAP-K3fdnhr6Z0W27LFQHaHa?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3','Apple iPhone 17 ',90000.00,3,'APL-IP17-001',159,'Mobiles'),(8,'Improve your strength and fitness with this Multi-Functional Push-Up Board. Designed with a color-coded system, it helps target different muscle groups including chest, shoulders, triceps, and back. The durable board comes with anti-slip grips and comfortable handles for a safe and effective workout. Compact and easy to use, it is perfect for home workouts, gym sessions, and fitness enthusiasts of all levels. Build muscle, improve posture, and enhance your overall fitness with this versatile training tool.',12,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71djsf74vAL._AC_UL320_.jpg','Multi-Functional Push-Up Board with Handles',1500.00,3,'FIT-PUSHUP-001',55,'Fitness'),(9,'Enjoy superior sound quality with the Sennheiser HD Closed-Back Wired Headphones, designed for immersive audio and long-lasting comfort. Featuring a closed-back design, these headphones provide excellent noise isolation, allowing you to focus on your music without distractions. Equipped with high-quality drivers, they deliver clear highs, detailed mids, and deep bass for an enhanced listening experience. The adjustable headband and soft ear cushions ensure a comfortable fit for extended use. Perfect for music, gaming, and professional audio needs.',10,'https://tse3.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP.lg84NQFeNBijqXpXZt7ihQHaLY?w=122&h=188&c=7&r=0&o=7&pid=1.7&rm=3','Sennheiser HD Closed-Back Wired Headphones',7999.00,3,'SEN-HD-CB-001',58,'Audio'),(10,'Upgrade your casual style with the Puma Men\'s Graphic Knit Vest, designed for comfort and modern streetwear appeal. Made from soft and breathable knit fabric, this vest ensures all-day comfort while maintaining a stylish fit. Featuring a bold graphic design and signature Puma branding, it adds a sporty edge to your outfit. Perfect for layering over t-shirts or shirts, this versatile vest is ideal for casual outings, gym wear, or everyday fashion.',15,'https://images.puma.com/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto,b_rgb:fafafa,w_600,h_600/global/632496/87/mod01/fnd/IND/fmt/png/Special-Items-Men\'s-Graphic-Knit-Vest','Puma Men\'s Graphic Knit Vest',2999.00,3,'PUMA-VEST-001',29,'Fashion'),(11,'Restore balance and hydration to your hair and scalp with the Moroccanoil Scalp Balancing Conditioner. Specially formulated with nourishing ingredients and antioxidant-rich argan oil, this conditioner helps soothe the scalp while improving hair texture and manageability. It deeply moisturizes without weighing hair down, leaving it soft, smooth, and refreshed. Ideal for all hair types, especially those experiencing dryness or scalp imbalance, this conditioner supports healthy, vibrant-looking hair with every use.',10,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61VgGCzyvML._AC_UL320_.jpg','Moroccanoil Scalp Balancing Conditioner (250ml)',2200.00,3,'MORO-CON-250-001',18,'Beauty'),(12,'Keep your skin soft, smooth, and glowing with this Hydrating Face Moisturizer Cream. Enriched with skin-loving ingredients, it deeply nourishes and hydrates while improving skin texture and elasticity. Suitable for all skin types, this lightweight and non-greasy formula absorbs quickly, making it perfect for daily use. It helps reduce dryness, enhances natural glow, and provides long-lasting moisture for healthy-looking skin.',15,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51q5C-l-n0L._AC_UL320_.jpg','Hydrating Face Moisturizer Cream',899.00,3,'BEAUTY-SKIN-001',60,'Beauty'),(13,'Boil water quickly and efficiently with the Rapid Electric Kettle 1.8L, designed for modern homes and workplaces. Powered by a 1500W heating element, it ensures fast boiling for tea, coffee, and instant meals. The stainless steel interior provides durability and safe usage, while the wide mouth design allows easy cleaning and filling.\nEquipped with an auto shut-off feature and boil-dry protection, it ensures maximum safety during use. The cool-touch handle and single-touch lid lock provide convenience and ease of handling. Compact and portable, this kettle is perfect for home, office, or travel use.',15,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51lYFOP2mUL._AC_UL320_.jpg','Rapid Electric Kettle 1.8L',1299.00,3,'KET-EL-1800-001',85,'Home'),(14,'Keep your surroundings fresh and pleasant with the Godrej aer Matic Automatic Air Freshener Kit. Designed for convenience, this smart air freshener automatically releases fragrance at regular intervals, ensuring continuous freshness in your room.\nIt features adjustable spray settings, allowing you to control intensity based on your preference. The easy-to-use design with a refillable system makes it ideal for homes, offices, bathrooms, and living spaces. With long-lasting fragrance and a modern stylish look, it enhances both atmosphere and décor effortlessly.',10,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71J+zbpd+0L._AC_UL320_.jpg','Godrej aer Matic Automatic Air Freshener Kit',599.00,3,'GOD-AER-001',48,'Home'),(15,'Level up your fitness routine with the Fashnex Resistance Bands Set, a complete workout solution for strength training, stretching, and toning. This versatile kit includes multiple resistance bands, foam handles, ankle straps, a door anchor, and a convenient carry bag, making it perfect for both home and outdoor workouts.\nDesigned for men and women of all fitness levels, the bands provide adjustable resistance for a variety of exercises targeting arms, legs, chest, back, and core. Made from high-quality, durable materials, they ensure safety and long-lasting use. Compact and easy to carry, this set is ideal for gym, home workouts, yoga, and travel fitness routines.',15,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81qm4oobKqL._AC_UL320_.jpg','Fashnex Resistance Bands Set with Accessories',1299.00,3,'FIT-RES-BAND-001',39,'Fitness'),(16,'Experience smooth performance and modern design with the OnePlus Nord CE6 Lite. Powered by an efficient processor and 5G connectivity, this smartphone ensures fast performance for everyday tasks, streaming, and gaming.\nIt features a large, vibrant display for an immersive viewing experience and a high-resolution camera system that captures stunning photos and videos. With ample storage, long-lasting battery life, and fast charging support, it keeps up with your daily needs effortlessly.\nDesigned with a sleek and stylish finish, the OnePlus Nord CE6 Lite offers a perfect combination of performance, elegance, and value for money.',10,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61T18EfkX0L._AC_UY218_.jpg','OnePlus Nord CE6 Lite (5G, 128GB)',18999.00,3,'ONEPLUS-CE6-001',30,'Mobiles'),(17,'Upgrade your meeting experience with the EMEET Bluetooth Speakerphone M3, a professional conference speaker designed for crystal-clear communication. Equipped with 4 AI-powered microphones, it offers 360° voice pickup, ensuring everyone in the room is heard clearly.\nWith Zoom certification and seamless compatibility with platforms like Microsoft Teams, it delivers reliable performance for online meetings. The speaker supports both Bluetooth and USB connectivity, making it flexible for various devices. Its daisy-chain feature allows expansion for larger groups of up to 20 people.\nFeaturing up to 18 hours of talk time, a compact design, and easy portability, the EMEET M3 is perfect for offices, remote work, and business travel.\n',10,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/7121X0dYMJL._AC_UL320_.jpg','EMEET Bluetooth Speakerphone M3 ',8999.00,3,'EMEET-M3-001',9,'Audio'),(18,'Experience advanced technology and sleek design with the Vivo V70. Built for modern users, this smartphone offers smooth performance powered by an efficient 5G processor, making multitasking, gaming, and streaming seamless.\nIt features a vibrant high-resolution display that delivers crisp visuals and an immersive viewing experience. The advanced camera system captures detailed photos and videos, perfect for everyday photography. With a long-lasting battery and fast charging support, the Vivo V70 ensures you stay connected throughout the day.\nElegant, powerful, and reliable, the Vivo V70 is a great choice for users looking for performance and style in one device.',15,'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcR89hC5CWMGi0XcR4CuxzXMQRQSJi9LkG5JXg&s','Vivo V70 (5G Smartphone, 128GB)',30000.00,4,'VIVO-V70-001',40,'Mobiles'),(19,'ed for immersive audio and ultimate comfort. Featuring advanced Active Noise Cancellation, these earbuds block out unwanted noise while Transparency mode lets you stay aware of your surroundings.\nEquipped with high-quality drivers, AirPods Pro deliver rich bass, crisp highs, and balanced sound for music, calls, and entertainment. The ergonomic in-ear design ensures a secure and comfortable fit for all-day use.\nWith seamless Apple device connectivity, touch controls, and a compact wireless charging case, these earbuds provide convenience, portability, and long-lasting battery life. Ideal for daily use, travel, workouts, and professional calls.',20,'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b9/AirPods_Pro_3_with_case.jpg','Apple AirPods Pro (Wireless Earbuds with Charging Case)',24000.00,4,'APL-AIRPODS-003',35,'Audio'),(20,'Upgrade your everyday style with these Men’s Slim Fit Cargo Pants in a trendy olive green shade. Designed for both functionality and fashion, these pants feature multiple spacious pockets, making them perfect for carrying essentials on the go.\nCrafted from durable and breathable fabric, they provide all-day comfort while ensuring a modern slim-fit look. The versatile design makes them suitable for casual outings, travel, streetwear, or outdoor activities. Pair them with t-shirts, hoodies, or jackets for a stylish and rugged appearance.',15,'https://www.urbanofashion.com/cdn/shop/files/jeanlscargo-03-olivegrn-1_181b3da2-76c2-456a-9345-ada2adfa3762.jpg?v=1771341264','Men’s Slim Fit Cargo Pants (Olive Green)',1999.00,4,'CRG-PANT-001',70,'Fashion'),(21,'Enhance your beauty with the Maybelline Creamy Matte Lipstick, designed to deliver intense color with a smooth matte finish. Its creamy formula glides effortlessly onto the lips, providing rich pigmentation and long-lasting wear without drying.\nInfused with moisturizing ingredients, it keeps your lips soft, hydrated, and comfortable throughout the day. Perfect for both everyday wear and special occasions, this lipstick adds a bold and stylish touch to your makeup look. Available in a variety of stunning shades to match your style.',10,'https://cloudinary.images-iherb.com/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto:eco/images/mby/mby56677/y/19.jpg','Maybelline Creamy Matte Lipstick',699.00,4,'MBL-LIP-001',39,'Beauty'),(22,'Upgrade your kitchen with the American Micronic Microwave Oven, designed for fast and convenient cooking. This versatile appliance supports multiple cooking modes such as heating, grilling, and baking, making it ideal for preparing a wide variety of dishes.\nWith user-friendly controls and preset cooking options, it ensures hassle-free operation for everyday use. The spacious interior accommodates different food sizes, while the durable build ensures long-lasting performance.\nPerfect for busy households, this microwave oven helps you cook delicious meals quickly while saving time and effort.',15,'https://americanmicronic.in/cdn/shop/files/71GlFzWcdfL._SL1500.jpg?v=1722594630&width=2048','American Micronic Microwave Oven (Convection/Grill)',8999.00,4,'MW-OVEN-001',45,'Home'),(23,'Strengthen your body and build muscle with this Hex Dumbbells Set, designed for effective home and gym workouts. Featuring a durable rubber-coated design, these dumbbells protect floors while ensuring a firm and secure grip during exercises.\nThe hexagonal shape prevents rolling, making them safe and convenient to use. Ideal for a wide range of workouts including strength training, toning, weight lifting, and full-body exercises. Suitable for beginners as well as advanced fitness enthusiasts, these dumbbells help improve strength, balance, and endurance.\nCompact, sturdy, and versatile, they are a must-have for your fitness setup.\n',20,'https://nwscdn.com/media/catalog/product/cache/h900xw900/f/o/forza-hex-dumbbells-main.jpg','Hex Dumbbells Set (Rubber Coated Gym Weights)',2999.00,4,'FIT-DUMB-001',30,'Fitness'),(24,'Experience innovation like never before with the Nothing Phone (1), a smartphone designed to stand out with its unique transparent back and Glyph interface lighting. Powered by a capable processor and 5G connectivity, it delivers smooth performance for everyday use, gaming, and multitasking.\nThe phone features a vibrant OLED display with a high refresh rate for a fluid and immersive viewing experience. Its dual-camera system captures sharp photos and detailed videos, while the optimized software ensures a clean and fast user experience.\nWith a long-lasting battery, fast charging support, and a stylish, futuristic design, the Nothing Phone (1) is perfect for users who want both performance and individuality in their smartphone.',20,'https://www.gizmochina.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Nothing-phone-1-500x500.jpg?x10805','Nothing Phone (1) (5G Smartphone, 128GB)',32999.00,4,'NOTHING-PHONE-001',60,'Mobiles'),(25,'Experience high-quality sound with these Wireless Over-Ear Bluetooth Headphones, designed for comfort and performance. Featuring powerful audio drivers, they deliver deep bass, clear vocals, and an immersive listening experience for music, calls, and entertainment.\nThe ergonomic over-ear design with soft cushioned ear cups ensures long-lasting comfort during extended use. With seamless Bluetooth connectivity, you can easily pair them with smartphones, laptops, and other devices.\nEquipped with a long-lasting battery and easy-to-use controls, these headphones are perfect for travel, work, gaming, and everyday use.',15,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61RahTQtAqL._AC_UF1000,1000_QL80_.jpg','Wireless Over-Ear Bluetooth Headphones',2999.00,4,'WH-HEAD-001',35,'Audio'),(26,'Upgrade your everyday style with this Men’s Slim Fit Check Shirt in a stylish steel grey pattern. Crafted from high-quality breathable fabric, it ensures all-day comfort while maintaining a sharp and modern look.\nFeaturing a classic check design, button-down front, and tailored slim fit, this shirt is perfect for both casual and semi-formal occasions. Pair it effortlessly with jeans or trousers for a smart and versatile outfit. Ideal for office wear, outings, and daily fashion.',15,'https://bananaclub.co.in/cdn/shop/files/DobbySteelGreyCheckShirt_1.jpg?v=1738823345&width=1000','Men’s Slim Fit Check Shirt (Steel Grey)',1499.00,4,'SHIRT-CHK-001',60,'Fashion'),(27,'Create flawless looks with this All-in-One Makeup Kit Set, perfect for both beginners and professionals. This complete set includes essential makeup products such as eyeshadows, lip colors, blush, and more, allowing you to experiment with a variety of styles.\nDesigned with high-quality, long-lasting formulas, the products provide smooth application and vibrant pigmentation. Compact and easy to carry, this kit is ideal for everyday use, travel, and special occasions.\nWhether you want a natural look or a bold glam style, this versatile makeup kit has everything you need to enhance your beauty.',15,'https://rukminim2.flixcart.com/image/480/640/xif0q/makeup-kit/s/3/v/-original-imagwfw3hteyxyf9.jpeg?q=90','All-in-One Makeup Kit Set',1299.00,4,'MAKE-KIT-001',39,'Beauty'),(28,'Make your kitchen tasks easier with the Wonderchef Mixer Grinder, a powerful and versatile appliance designed for everyday cooking needs. Equipped with a high-performance motor, it efficiently handles grinding, blending, and mixing ingredients with ease.\nFeaturing multiple jars for different uses, it is perfect for preparing smoothies, chutneys, spices, and batters. The durable stainless-steel blades ensure consistent performance, while the sturdy design provides long-lasting use.\nWith easy-to-use controls and a compact design, this mixer grinder is ideal for modern kitchens, helping you save time and effort while preparing delicious meals.',20,'https://www.wonderchef.com/cdn/shop/files/Image-01_802b73ab-ac59-497c-b6b7-6ad9ce744391.jpg?v=1766044704','Wonderchef Mixer Grinder (Multi-Purpose Kitchen Appliance)',4499.00,4,'MIX-GRIND-001',39,'Home'),(29,'Build stronger wrists and forearms with this Forearm Strengthener Wrist Roller Equipment, designed for effective muscle training and grip improvement. Ideal for fitness enthusiasts, athletes, and beginners, this tool helps enhance strength, endurance, and flexibility in the arms.\nMade from durable and high-quality materials, it ensures stability and long-lasting performance during workouts. The ergonomic design offers a comfortable grip, making it easy to use at home, gym, or even while traveling.\nPerfect for strength training, rehabilitation exercises, and improving grip power, this compact equipment is a must-have addition to your fitness routine.',15,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51u6-BviWDL._AC_UF894,1000_QL80_.jpg','Forearm Strengthener Wrist Roller Equipment',799.00,4,'FIT-FOREARM-001',30,'Fitness'),(30,'Turn any gathering into a party with the JYX Boat Karaoke Bluetooth Speaker, designed for music lovers and entertainment enthusiasts. This powerful speaker comes with dual wireless microphones, making it perfect for karaoke sessions, parties, and events.\nFeaturing high-quality sound output with deep bass and clear vocals, it delivers an immersive audio experience. The dazzling LED light effects enhance the party vibe, while Bluetooth connectivity ensures seamless pairing with smartphones and other devices.\nWith an IPX5 waterproof design, it is suitable for both indoor and outdoor use. The included remote control adds convenience, and the long-lasting battery keeps your music going for hours. Ideal for home parties, outdoor trips, and celebrations.',20,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81rQp0++rqL._AC_UY218_.jpg','JYX Boat Karaoke Bluetooth Speaker with Dual Microphones',11999.00,2,'SPKR-KARAOKE-001',79,'Audio'),(31,'The Realme Narzo 80 Pro 5G is a powerful smartphone designed for speed and performance. With 12GB RAM and 256GB storage, it easily handles multitasking, gaming, and heavy apps. The 5G connectivity ensures fast internet for smooth streaming and browsing. It comes with a bright display for an immersive viewing experience and a high-quality camera for clear photos and videos. The long-lasting battery with fast charging keeps you powered all day, while the stylish Speed Silver design gives it a premium look.',30,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71J+dpjrzhL._AC_UY218_.jpg','Realme Narzo 80 Pro 5G (12GB RAM, 256GB Storage)  ',25999.00,2,'REALME-N80PRO-001 ',76,'Mobiles'),(32,'Upgrade your wardrobe with this Men’s Stylish Cotton Blend Casual Shirt, designed for comfort and everyday elegance. Made from a breathable cotton blend fabric, it offers a soft feel and ensures all-day comfort. The full sleeve design with a button-down front and dual flap pockets adds a trendy and functional touch to your look.\nPerfect for casual office wear, outings, or daily use, this shirt combines style and versatility effortlessly. Its modern fit and classic design make it easy to pair with jeans or trousers, giving you a smart and confident appearance wherever you go.',60,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61H1HxfTAUL._AC_UL320_.jpg','Men’s Stylish Cotton Blend Casual Shirt (Full Sleeve)',498.00,2,'SHIRT-CASUAL-002',98,'Fashion'),(33,'Get intensely hydrated and smooth hair with the L\'Oréal Paris Hyaluron Moisture 72H Conditioner, powered by Hyaluronic Acid. This advanced formula helps retain moisture in your hair for up to 72 hours, leaving it soft, shiny, and manageable.\nLightweight and non-greasy, it deeply nourishes dry and dehydrated hair without weighing it down. It helps reduce frizz, improves texture, and adds a healthy bounce. Perfect for everyday use, this conditioner is ideal for anyone looking to restore moisture and achieve silky, salon-like hair at home.',20,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/511fPrnY+bL._AC_UL320_.jpg','L\'Oréal Paris Hyaluron Moisture 72H',241.00,2,' LOREAL-CON-001',13,'Beauty'),(34,'Enhance your bedroom décor with the BSB HOME Cotton Feel Double Bed Bedsheet Set, designed for comfort and style. Made with soft and breathable fabric (144 thread count), this bedsheet ensures a smooth and cozy sleeping experience.\nFeaturing a refreshing mint green floral print, it adds a touch of elegance and freshness to your room. The set includes a double bedsheet along with two matching pillow covers, making it a complete bedding solution.\nDurable, easy to maintain, and gentle on the skin, this bedsheet is perfect for everyday use, offering both comfort and aesthetic appeal.',15,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61KGM6EmuzL._AC_UL320_.jpg','BSB HOME Cotton Feel Double Bed',249.00,2,'BEDSHEET-002',20,'Home'),(35,'Upgrade your home workouts with the PowerMax Fitness TDA-96 Treadmill, designed for high performance and convenience. Powered by a strong 4HP motor, it delivers smooth and efficient running sessions suitable for walking, jogging, and intense workouts.\nFeaturing auto incline functionality, it allows you to simulate real outdoor running conditions and increase workout intensity. The treadmill supports up to 110kg user weight and includes 12 pre-set workout programs to suit different fitness levels.\nEquipped with Bluetooth connectivity, you can enjoy music and track your fitness progress through a mobile app. The LED display shows essential workout data like speed, time, distance, and calories burned. ',29,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71jhc1QkgsL._AC_UL320_.jpg','PowerMax Fitness TDA-96 Auto Incline',24900.00,2,'READ-001',24,'Fitness'),(36,'Upgrade your everyday style with these Men’s Regular Fit Stretchable Jeans, designed for comfort and a classic look. Featuring a mid-rise waist and stretchable fabric, these jeans provide a perfect fit and ease of movement for all-day wear.\nThe timeless design makes them suitable for casual outings, office wear, and daily use. Crafted from durable material, these jeans offer long-lasting performance while maintaining a stylish appearance. Pair them with t-shirts or shirts for a versatile and smart look.',20,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/61dFcpPdJkL._AC_UL320_.jpg','Men’s Regular Fit Stretchable Jeans (Mid Rise)',499.00,3,'JEANS-MEN-001',109,'Fashion'),(37,'Duo 3 5G smartphone featuring modern design, dual display concept, 5G connectivity, smooth performance, and long battery life.',10,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/5180s4x0XXL._AC_UY218_.jpg','Lava Blaze Duo 3 5G',19000.00,2,'LB-DUO3-5G',14,'Mobiles'),(38,'Premium silicone strap designed for Apple Watch. Lightweight, durable, and sweat-resistant with a comfortable fit. Compatible with Apple Watch Series 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, SE, and Ultra (adjust size as needed). Ideal for daily wear, workouts, and outdoor use.',25,'https://store.storeimages.cdn-apple.com/4982/as-images.apple.com/is/watch-bands-header-202209?wid=1600&hei=960&fmt=jpeg&qlt=90&.v=1660679601144','Apple Watch Silicone Strap',3000.00,3,'AWS-SIL-001',21,'Fashion');
